body:
This PR is a follow-up to the issue with missing pileup in DTs in premixing from couple months ago (that was fixed in #23091). If the parameter overrides would not have had the explicit types, we would have caught the problem (inconsistent parameters) already with the PR that introduced the bug. To prevent similar incidents in the future, this PR removes all explicit right-hand-side types from `DigiToRawDM_cff.py`.

Tested in 10_2_0_pre6, no changes expected.

@mdhildreth @kpedro88
